    </h2>
<pre xml:space="preserve">     Dweller in yon dungeon dark,
     Hangman of creation! mark,
     Who in widow-weeds appears,
     Laden with unhonour'd years,
     Noosing with care a bursting purse,
     Baited with many a deadly curse?
