    <h2>
      Fragment,—Why, Why Tell The Lover
    </h2>
<pre xml:space="preserve">     Tune—“Caledonian Hunt's delight.”
 </pre>
<pre xml:space="preserve">     Why, why tell thy lover
     Bliss he never must enjoy”?
     Why, why undeceive him,
     And give all his hopes the lie?
     O why, while fancy, raptur'd slumbers,
     Chloris, Chloris all the theme,
     Why, why would'st thou, cruel—
     Wake thy lover from his dream?
</pre>
    <p>
      <a name="link2H_4_0532" id="link2H_4_0532">
